'''&quot;The Ghost of Harrenhal&quot;''' is the fifth episode of the [[Season 2|second season]] of ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. It is the fifteenth episode of the series overall. It premiered on April 29, 2012. It was written by executive producers [[David Benioff]] and [[D.B. Weiss]] and directed by [[David Petrarca]].

